The right kind of nerds...

We’re normal enough to know how to talk to people, but nerdy enough to know how it all works...

Meet the Team

AL ELLIOTT: Head Nerd

Al’s an author, speaker and entrepreneur, and lives for all things techy. He’s been building websites since 2002, both for his own businesses and private clients.

As an accomplished copywriter, CRM geek, Email expert and web developer, most of our work is overseen by Al (of course, he complains, but he wouldn’t have it any other way…).

CHRIS JENKINS: Keeper of Promises

Chris is operations through and through. He understands how businesses work, and holds the world record for ‘Number of Pieces of Paper on One Desk at Any One Time’.

Despite his sensible approach to business, he’s creative, highly-intelligent and exactly the kind of person you want on your team when brainstorming project ideas.

LEANNE ELLIOTT: Resident Psychologist

Leanne is not only a Psychologist and expert in human behaviour, but a brilliant organiser and formidable project manager. She has an almost photographic memory for dates & figures.

When she’s not bringing order to our ramblings, she’ll have her phone glued to her ear, whilst sending emails, making sandwiches, correcting typos and putting her husband in his place (see Al’s surname above for a clue…).
